snippet.title: Wavetale - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description: Wavetale is a story-driven, third-person action-adventure platformer, set in an island world built atop the remains of a once magnificent city. This new gameplay trailer shows off the game alongside revealing a release date for all platforms.
